    "Check my first exercise for details. Basically you need\n",
    "\n",
    "- Python on your system\n",
    "- Start with an empty _project_ directory; then copy `requirements.txt`, `setup.bat`, `run.bat`, and `fruitfind.ipynb` into it.\n",
